<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_f5bed337-32d7-458a-81a9-750bc7333218" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>B6P2</sptc><title id="_146a6d78-a84e-4bb5-ba40-163262d1ed90">Velocity</title><archive-num>2019: BP6.2</archive-num><subclause id="_d2c26824-eb85-4544-8b3c-51ff7535a74b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_78694538-c510-4e60-aa44-b299d3fb23d5">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Water velocity within the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1422_4.4.0.xml#_bd764954-3054-4109-81f2-164feefc5058" id="_88f9ac73-a809-4b06-a0c1-7491f60fd8bb" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">rainwater service</xref> pipework must not exceed 3 m/s for no less than 99% of the time that water is required during the peak hour. </p></subclause><callout id="_3141804d-9308-479b-8d01-949a7135e19e"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>During the hour of heaviest usage in reticulated <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1422_4.4.0.xml#_bd764954-3054-4109-81f2-164feefc5058" id="_2b17258a-3caf-4b73-81fe-564f9132251c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">rainwater service</xref> pipework, a velocity of 3 m/s must not be exceeded for 99% of the time that any downstream fixture is in use.</p></callout></clause>